OL,3,CPolice officers who shot man dead in
OL,4,CCarlisle granted anonymity
OL,6,FPolice officers involved in the fatal
OL,7,Fshooting of 40-year-old man cannot be
OL,8,Fidentified, a coroner has ruled.
OL,10,FAt a pre-inquest hearing held in
OL,11,FCockermouth, Coroner Kirsty Gomersal
OL,12,Fsaid that two police officers
OL,13,Fidentified only as Officer C and
OL,14,FOfficer L would be granted anonymity,
OL,15,Fwhen an inquest into the death of 40-
OL,16,Fyear-old Sergii Kuzmenko takes place.
