OL,6,FShe also said the officers should give
OL,7,Ftheir evidence behind a screen and
OL,8,Fwill be seen only by the coroner,
OL,9,Fadvocates and a Ukrainian translator
OL,10,Ffor Mr Kuzmenko's family.
OL,12,FFour additional officers known only as
OL,13,FOfficers B, D, M and P will also be
OL,14,Fgranted anonymity to prevent officers
OL,15,FC and L being identified
OL,16,Funintentionally.
