OL,3,CPolice officers who shot man dead in
OL,4,CCarlisle granted anonymity
OL,6,FCumbria Constabulary firearms officers
OL,7,Fwere called to an address on Borland
OL,8,FAvenue in Carlisle at around 3.30pm on
OL,9,FMonday 19 December 2022. It had been
OL,10,Freported that a man was making threats
OL,11,Fto kill and young children were
OL,12,Fpresent.
OL,14,FOnce inside, officers identified an
OL,15,Fimminent threat to a child and two
OL,16,Fofficers shot and killed Sergii
OL,17,FKuzmenko. He died from multiple
OL,18,Fgunshot wounds.
